### Salud
GET http://localhost:8000/health/live

### Capacidades (sin secretos)
GET http://localhost:8000/capabilities

### Probar conexión a Google Drive
POST http://localhost:8000/connections/google-drive/test

### Probar conexión FTP/FTPS
POST http://localhost:8000/connections/ftp/test

### Crear snapshot completo
POST http://localhost:8000/discovery-runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "root_folder_id": "TU_FOLDER_ID_AQUI"
}

### Crear snapshot parcial (primera ola prioritaria)
POST http://localhost:8000/discovery-runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "folder_ids": ["FOLDER_ID_1", "FOLDER_ID_2"]
}

### Buscar elementos en un snapshot
GET http://localhost:8000/snapshots/SNAPSHOT_ID/items/search?text=informe&item_type=FILE

### Crear un lote de migración
POST http://localhost:8000/migration-batches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "snapshot_id": "SNAPSHOT_ID",
  "name": "Primera ola - contratos",
  "priority": 100
}

### Agregar un selector (carpeta recursiva)
POST http://localhost:8000/migration-batches/BATCH_ID/selectors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "kind": "FOLDER_RECURSIVE",
  "value": "FOLDER_ID",
  "include": true
}

### Excluir un elemento específico
POST http://localhost:8000/migration-batches/BATCH_ID/selectors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "kind": "EXPLICIT_IDS",
  "value": "ITEM_ID_A_EXCLUIR",
  "include": false
}

### Generar el plan (dry-run: no escribe en FTP)
POST http://localhost:8000/migration-batches/BATCH_ID/plan

### Ver la vista previa antes de ejecutar
GET http://localhost:8000/migration-batches/BATCH_ID/preview

### Ver elementos pendientes de revisión de nombre
GET http://localhost:8000/migration-batches/BATCH_ID/name-reviews

### Sobrescribir manualmente un nombre destino
PATCH http://localhost:8000/migration-items/ITEM_ID/destination-name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "new_base_name": "147_INF_BIM_V02",
  "changed_by": "brayan6264@gmail.com"
}

### Aprobar un nombre en revisión
POST http://localhost:8000/migration-items/ITEM_ID/approve-name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "changed_by": "brayan6264@gmail.com"
}

### Iniciar la migración (procesa de forma síncrona hasta max_items elementos)
POST http://localhost:8000/migration-batches/BATCH_ID/start?max_items=20

### Ver estado del lote
GET http://localhost:8000/migration-batches/BATCH_ID/status

### Ver el reporte final
GET http://localhost:8000/migration-batches/BATCH_ID/report

### Reintentar los elementos fallidos
POST http://localhost:8000/migration-batches/BATCH_ID/retry-failed
